<p>The more news pattern is for showing a list of news articles or blog posts. These are previous posts or articles that are not featured items.</p>

<ul>
	<li>There must a thumbnail image, use a placeholder if an image is not available.</li>
	<li>The thumbnail image must always be on the right.</li>
	<li>Thumbnail image must be 360px by 240px.</li>
	<li>There must not be more than 40 words in the excerpt and it must end with the ellipses character <code>&amp;hellip;</code> (&hellip;).</li>
	<li>There should not be more than 10 items on one page, more than that must use <a href="../pagination/index.html">pagination</a>.</li>
</ul>

